    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――どりきゅんのレッスン中",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――During DoriKyun's lesson",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 3.1000000912
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_07_05/sud_vo_adv_main_03_07_05-ktn001.m4a",
      "text": "ん……くぅっ、はっ、はっ……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ugh… Gasp‚ gasp…!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 3.1000000912,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 6.7517688392
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "lim",
      "speakerName": "小南来夢",
      "speakerNameEn": "Laim",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-lim.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_07_05/sud_vo_adv_main_03_07_05-lim001.m4a",
      "text": "ほら、またステップが遅れてる！　こののろまが！！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hey‚ your steps are slow again! You slowpoke!!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 6.7517688392,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 11.6780727664
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_07_05/sud_vo_adv_main_03_07_05-ktn002.m4a",
      "text": "はっ、はいっ！　く、ぅぅ……っ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Y-Yes! Ugh…!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 11.6780727664,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 16.6125625569
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "lmn",
      "speakerName": "大須賀れもん",
      "speakerNameEn": "Lemon",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-lmn.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_07_05/sud_vo_adv_main_03_07_05-lmn001.m4a",
      "text": "疲れは一切顔に出さないように\nライブ後半でファンに醜態を晒したいの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Don’t let any fatigue show on your face.\nDo you want to make a fool of yourself in front of your fans?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 19.9000000475,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 23.3868255256
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_07_05/sud_vo_adv_main_03_07_05-ktn003.m4a",
      "text": "すみ、ません……っ！　はっ、はっ……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m s-sorry…! Gasp‚ gasp…!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 23.3868255256,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 29.0518368362
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "lim",
      "speakerName": "小南来夢",
      "speakerNameEn": "Laim",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-lim.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_07_05/sud_vo_adv_main_03_07_05-lim002.m4a",
      "text": "うし、この曲に合わせるのはこんなもんでいいか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Alright‚ that’s enough for this song.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 30.1185050288,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_07_05/sud_vo_adv_main_03_07_05-ktn004.m4a",
      "text": "は、はい……っ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Y-Yes…!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 34.8317929227,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 37.4368948101
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_07_05/sud_vo_adv_main_03_07_05-ktn005.m4a",
      "text": "（まさか、ここまで基礎に差があるなんて……っ）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(I can’t believe there’s such a difference in our basics…!)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 37.4368948101,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 42.0867347518
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_07_05/sud_vo_adv_main_03_07_05-ktn006.m4a",
      "text": "（れもんさんも、来夢さんも、あれだけ激しく動いても）\n（息一つ切らしてない）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(Lemon-san and Laim-san aren’t even out of breath)\n(even after moving so intensely.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 46.1983902191,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 48.4448981721
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_unrest-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 51.7666667142
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "lim",
      "speakerName": "小南来夢",
      "speakerNameEn": "Laim",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-lim.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_07_05/sud_vo_adv_main_03_07_05-lim003.m4a",
      "text": "……ちっ。やっぱこの程度か\nこれじゃその辺のアイドルと大して変わんねぇな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Tsk. This is all you’ve got?\nYou’re no different from any other idol out there.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 51.7666667142,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 55.2925397038
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_07_05/sud_vo_adv_main_03_07_05-ktn007.m4a",
      "text": "……どういうことですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…What do you mean?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 55.2925397038,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 56.9502721349
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "lmn",
      "speakerName": "大須賀れもん",
      "speakerNameEn": "Lemon",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-lmn.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_07_05/sud_vo_adv_main_03_07_05-lmn002.m4a",
      "text": "琴乃。あなた……今私達に食らいつくことしか\n考えてなかったでしょ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Kotono. You… weren’t thinking of anything\nother than trying to keep up with us‚ were you?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 61.6000000475,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 63.7302962501
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_07_05/sud_vo_adv_main_03_07_05-ktn008.m4a",
      "text": "あ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 63.7302962501,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 65.0107560753
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "lim",
      "speakerName": "小南来夢",
      "speakerNameEn": "Laim",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-lim.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_07_05/sud_vo_adv_main_03_07_05-lim004.m4a",
      "text": "だからお前はあめぇんだよ\nあたしらに食らいつくのなんざ最低限も最低限だろ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s why you’re so naive.\nKeeping up with us is the bare minimum.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 67.8000000475,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "lmn",
      "speakerName": "大須賀れもん",
      "speakerNameEn": "Lemon",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-lmn.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_07_05/sud_vo_adv_main_03_07_05-lmn003.m4a",
      "text": "私達と体力勝負がしたくて、仲間を捨ててきたの？\nそんな訳ないわよね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Did you abandon your friends just to compete with us physically?\nThat can’t be true‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 76.8333333808,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 78.733000942
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_07_05/sud_vo_adv_main_03_07_05-ktn009.m4a",
      "text": "……はい、違います",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…No‚ it’s not.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 78.733000942,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 81.726130259
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "lmn",
      "speakerName": "大須賀れもん",
      "speakerNameEn": "Lemon",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-lmn.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_07_05/sud_vo_adv_main_03_07_05-lmn004.m4a",
      "text": "バカげた量の練習をこなす中で\n観客を魅了するパフォーマンスを常に意識すること",
      "translations": {
        "en": "While going through a ridiculous amount of practice‚\nalways be conscious of captivating the audience with your performance.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 84.3333333808,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 88.2241576473
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "lim",
      "speakerName": "小南来夢",
      "speakerNameEn": "Laim",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-lim.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_07_05/sud_vo_adv_main_03_07_05-lim005.m4a",
      "text": "発する声の一音一音、動かした指の一本一本まで\n神経を張り巡らせるんだよ。一秒だって油断すんな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Focus your nerves on every single sound you make‚\nevery single finger you move. Don’t let your guard down for a second.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 93.2333333808,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 97.9000000475
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_serious-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 100.0338124235
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 100.0338124235
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "lmn",
      "speakerName": "大須賀れもん",
      "speakerNameEn": "Lemon",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-lmn.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_07_05/sud_vo_adv_main_03_07_05-lmn005.m4a",
      "text": "……今、「それくらい意識してるけど」って\n顔をしたわね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…You just made a face that said‚\n\"I'm already aware of that‚\" didn’t you?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 103.4333288032,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 105.2161707521
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "lim",
      "speakerName": "小南来夢",
      "speakerNameEn": "Laim",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-lim.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_07_05/sud_vo_adv_main_03_07_05-lim006.m4a",
      "text": "それが出来てねぇから言ってんだよ、このへぼが\nどんだけ幸せな頭してんだ？　ああ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m saying this because you’re not doing it‚ you idiot.\nHow naive are you? Huh?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 109.4806198717,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "lmn",
      "speakerName": "大須賀れもん",
      "speakerNameEn": "Lemon",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-lmn.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_07_05/sud_vo_adv_main_03_07_05-lmn006.m4a",
      "text": "中途半端なアイドルを全て叩き潰し、アイドル業界を\n変革させる……私達はそんな覚悟を持ってやってるの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We’re doing this with the determination to crush\nall the half-assed idols and revolutionize the idol industry.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 117.7247419636,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 122.9641977271
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "lmn",
      "speakerName": "大須賀れもん",
      "speakerNameEn": "Lemon",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-lmn.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_07_05/sud_vo_adv_main_03_07_05-lmn007.m4a",
      "text": "一緒に練習するなら、そのくらいの覚悟を持ちなさい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If you’re going to practice with us‚ come with that kind of resolve.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 122.9641977271,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 127.3060571314
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "lim",
      "speakerName": "小南来夢",
      "speakerNameEn": "Laim",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-lim.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_07_05/sud_vo_adv_main_03_07_05-lim007.m4a",
